
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-httpauth-scram-auth-15.txt'>
    <title>"Salted Challenge Response (SCRAM) HTTP Authentication Mechanism", Alexey Melnikov</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-httpauth-scram-auth-15.txt</link>
    <description>This specification describes a family of HTTP authentication mechanisms called the Salted Challenge Response Authentication Mechanism (SCRAM), which provides a more robust authentication mechanism than a plaintext password protected by Transport Layer Security (TLS) and avoids the deployment obstacles presented by earlier TLS-protected challenge response authentication mechanisms.</description>
    <dc:date>2015-12-16T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
